item.description:
Having had a great time last weekend, and with cooler weather approaching, its time again for another pick-up game of Ultimate Frisbee.

 

never played? No biggie, we're not into rules minutia, just a bit of fun and socializing interspersed with running and tossing a disc.

 

If there are fewer tan 6 RSVP's I will cancel it, and if it is actively raining or overly soggy, the same.
item.how_to_find_us: Meet at the Statue at the North End of the park, (closer to Westminster Street)
item.name: Ultimate Frisbee on a cool fall morning
